episodes.title: Street Debate: One Born Again  Christian V. 3 Jehovah's Witnesses
episodes.description:
Debate I had with 3 Jehovah's Witnesses at one of their carts. Subjects covered are: 144,000, Jesus as Mediator, Born again, The Deity of Jesus, Prayer to Jesus, relationship with Jesus.

Note, these videos are made in the public interest in a journalistic manner.

episodes.title: Debate with Jehovah's Witnesses in town centre 17/07/19
episodes.description:
Discussion I had today with two JWs in my local town on the subjects of: changing truth, Jesus' Mediatorship, The 2 Witness Rule, & Being Born Again.

Sorry, it's been a while since I uploaded last but have been struggling with some voice problems which has hindered outreach a little really.

Note, these videos are made in the public interest in a journalistic manner.
